HEADWORD: Quinovic
<hw>Qui*no"vic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or designating, a crystalline acid obtained from
some varieties of cinchona bark.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>chinovic</asp>, and <asp>kinovic</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
